<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>New Device Login Alert</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 15px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
      }
      .button-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }
      ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>New Device Login Detected! üîê</h2>

      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      <p>We noticed a login to your account from a new device or location:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ip}}</li>
        <li><strong>Device:</strong> {{device}}</li>
        <li><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</li>
        <li><strong>Date & Time:</strong> {{time}}</li>
      </ul>

      <p>If this was you, you can safely ignore this email. Otherwise, we
        recommend updating your password immediately.</p>

      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="{{securitySettingsUrl}}" class="btn">Check Account Security</a>
      </div>

      <p class="footer">
        Need help? Contact support at support@aestheticsconsults.com.au<br />
        &copy; {{year}} Aesthetics Consults. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
